msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Thanks for coming, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Yeah, no problem.\r\nShould we figure out where to go while we walk?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Sure!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "That boy there, I recognize him.\r\nHe's always cheering for me at my matches."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Oh, so he's one of your fans?\r\nWhy don't you go say hi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Mhm! ...Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Um... I don't have any more money..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Say what? Didn't we tell you that you'd\r\nhave to start dippin' into your mom's purse?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "You're not going back on the deal now, are ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "But... We're so poor,\r\nI can't take money from her..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Little bitch... You want more bruises then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "If you don't got the money, who's got the tab for\r\ntoday, huh? How you gonna make up for the loss?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "A crew of bullies, huh?\r\nScum of the earth..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Poor guy... Last time we talked, he mentioned\r\nhe was getting picked on by a bad crowd..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "At the time, I told him not to run away and face\r\nthem head on... But that was irresponsible, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "We have to help him!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "No, wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Sorry... But this behavior...\r\nCan't you guys shape up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Please... Stop doing it..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "Dumbass... Am I hearing this right?\r\nYou suddenly grow a pair?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "I... won't run from this anymore..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "That so?\r\nThen let's see where that gets you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "Hey, you want some too, old man!?\r\nThis ain't your concern, is it!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "You just made it my concern."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "This guy here... is a big fan of\r\nsomeone pretty special to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "What the fuck...!?\r\nFuck it, let's get this guy's cash!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "I-I can't believe this guy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Hey, if you ever corner this kid again, you're\r\ngonna be sorry... You wanna know how sorry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "N-Noooooo!!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Th-Thank you so much!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "No, I was only here because\r\nyou've been there for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "If you owe anyone, it's her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Saki-san!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Are you okay?\r\nYou're not hurt?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Yeah... Saki-san, I faced them head on,\r\njust like I told you I would!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I mean, it almost got me killed, but..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I didn't know how bad things were for\r\nyou, and I told you to face them like a fool..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "No, even if that's not what you'd told me,\r\nI probably would have stood up to them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "I saw your last match, Saki-san. You were up against\r\na huge foreigner, but you kept standing back up, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "You ended up losing that match...\r\nBut I was so inspired by you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Saki-san, you were so cool... I realized\r\nI had to stand up to them like you would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "So, even if you'd told me not to,\r\nI still had your example to follow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Saki-san... Thank you for giving me that courage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Right... Likewise."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "I'll be at your next match for sure!\r\nShow me the strength I know you've got, Saki-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Well, see ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Sounds like you're already a great wrestler, Saki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "Whether you won or lost... What's important is\r\nwhat you showed that kid through wrestling."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... I've never been so happy\r\nto be a professional wrestler."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry I ended up dragging you\r\ninto a fist fight, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Don't sweat it.\r\nI'm used to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Besides, you're a professional wrestler. Doesn't\r\nmatter who, you can't fight a civilian, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "So, what do you say we go back to our date, where\r\nyou can be the cheerful Saki you always are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Yeah...! Good call!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "But... Before we go...\r\nCan we have just a minute together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "Hm? Sure, I don't mind."
msgstr ""

